sg":"very thank 呢?"},{"pid":"7f969d1fa357c269b543f2c9f57fbf9aa276fb96","tid":863242,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:31:22.000Z","msg":"油站應該叫「Add Oil Station」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8ff4511f9d800083cef5aa493362e7efbd0c54","tid":863242,"uid":106426,"like":2,"dislike":221,"score":-219,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:32:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fdef047a7a3fb8a0274c52612a08cdb272e75be","tid":863242,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:34:46.000Z","msg":"連登殘廢餐：<br />\n<a href=\"https://public.oed.com/updates/new-words-list-september-2018/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.oed.com%2Fupdates%2Fnew-words-list-september-2018%2F&d=UtkUhT%2FKEs8vz8Ws9HYy%2Bo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=6a196463\" target=\"_blank\">https://public.oed.com/updates/new-words-list-september-2018/</a><br />\n<br />\nadd oil 係邊？"},{"pid":"a3a46fb8a1e6b6181893385bc2ee677fe0d817bb","tid":863242,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe66acfdda5c1f03fd01139a823493e186358cde","tid":863242,"uid":52215,"like":23,"dislike":5,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:15:31.000Z","msg":"下次輪到Holland bank cheque"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"Wenly Bank"},{"pid":"fe6d149121f042ff10bf28d91974a9566f58b18c","tid":863242,"uid":71568,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"0f8ff4511f9d800083cef5aa493362e7efbd0c54","tid":863242,"uid":106426,"like":2,"dislike":221,"score":-219,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:32:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:40:44.000Z","msg":"你都on9"},{"pid":"980a2fda372c922ef706526322faab783829921b","tid":863242,"uid":22054,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"0fdef047a7a3fb8a0274c52612a08cdb272e75be","tid":863242,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:34:46.000Z","msg":"連登殘廢餐：<br />\n<a href=\"https://public.oed.com/updates/new-words-list-september-2018/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.oed.com%2Fupdates%2Fnew-words-list-september-2018%2F&d=UtkUhT%2FKEs8vz8Ws9HYy%2Bo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=6a196463\" target=\"_blank\">https://public.oed.com/updates/new-words-list-september-2018/</a><br />\n<br />\nadd oil 係邊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:43:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://public.oed.com/appeals/add-oil-expressing-encouragement/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.oed.com%2Fappeals%2Fadd-oil-expressing-encouragement%2F&d=UtkUhT%2FKEs8vz8Ws9HYy%2Bo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=3cd8fbfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://public.oed.com/appeals/add-oil-expressing-encouragement/</a>"},{"pid":"0abd6c97fc2ee876055020e6a469b7e6a0c20789","tid":863242,"uid":194415,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:44:39.000Z","msg":"oed editor 求教連登仔起底：<br />\n<br />\nSo far, the earliest definitive evidence we have found is from the South China Morning Post of November 2005:<br />\n<br />\nWhen a mainland Chinese athlete stepped into the arena, some children mistakenly thought he represented Macau and started chanting: &lsquo;Macau team, add oil!&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n2005 South China Morning Post (Hong Kong) 1 November (Macau Notes section) p. 2<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">However, several sources suggest that the expression originated as a cheer at the Macau Grand Prix in the 1960s. Can you help find any printed examples of add oil from before November 2005?</span>"},{"pid":"75940b6a58d092fb14ff91ecb977fcd714848ffa","tid":863242,"uid":54161,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"1c4e1070ed523e2fb981a7a96631c8d77f5eeefc","tid":863242,"uid":2641,"like":426,"dislike":4,"score":422,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T12:28:26.000Z","msg":"邊個閪人話廣東話唔係世界潮流<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:49:43.000Z","msg":"其實佢唔取拼音就係對各個中文發音都公平"},{"pid":"66c5f8ff342b8806c14f7687565a1f1fcfbf7c96","tid":863242,"uid":92376,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:50:42.000Z","msg":"以後啲人可以用add oil考試了"},{"pid":"a16f038adbfc716ee722c8b838690ccc8fa9b65f","tid":863242,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:52:24.000Z","msg":"China add oil<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9d7841f1be618f3e9d9d423f2487e286908161","tid":863242,"uid":62950,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"66c5f8ff342b8806c14f7687565a1f1fcfbf7c96","tid":863242,"uid":92376,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:50:42.000Z","msg":"以後啲人可以用add oil考試了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c65d4d73642478e04d28c729571fa2726647258","tid":863242,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:53:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b87adc4008bb2c968541e6bd9ce0d36fe36f656","tid":863242,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1154257ba08fa1520afb93620acfe0390fd83a","tid":863242,"uid":1149,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"quote":{"pid":"66c5f8ff342b8806c14f7687565a1f1fcfbf7c96","tid":863242,"uid":92376,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T13:50:42.000Z","ms